title: Dells Irish situation is positive company set to hire - senior executive
text:
Dell's Irish situation is 'positive', company set to hire - senior executive 
Independent.ie Thursday 22nd October, 2015 
Dell's most senior Irish executive says that the company's Irish situation is "positive", with the company set to hire additional sales staff for its Dublin office.
